# Claude Code session state (per-user). Project-level skills are tracked.
# Pattern note: `.claude/` would prune the whole tree before any `!` rule
# can re-include children, so we match direct contents with `.claude/*` and
# then whitelist `skills/`.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/

# Local HA pod test snapshots
.ha-pod-backup/
scripts/ha-pod-deploy.sh

CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
